# Date Synchronization
- Synchronize dates across groups using `synchronizeGroupDates` in [src/utils/csvParser.ts](mdc:src/utils/csvParser.ts).
- Respect settings date range from `SettingsPanel` when provided.

# Horizontal Scrolling
- Use outer containers with `overflow-x-auto` and `scroll-smooth`.
- Only left gradient as scroll hint; never right.

# Platform-Country Grouping
- Group tables by `${platform}-${country}` key.
- Headers reorderable via DnD kit (React 19 compatible sensors).

# Table Layout Standards
- No internal table scrolling; dynamic width based on visible columns.
- Fixed font classes for headers and cells.
